snippet.title: Jokes on Demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 Notes

localized.description:
Peoples came out with their sadness through jokes and memes after demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes. Modi government has banned notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 to curb corruption and black money.
